    "body": "From @Exteris\r\n\r\nThe presence of `lmod` or `environment-modules` should be auto-detected and configured the first time Spack is run; just like we currently do for compilers in `compilers.yaml`.  Similarly, there is no point in routinely generating modules for a module system the user doesn't have installed.\r\n",
